title: Tank and TK Interview and More
itunes:title: Tank and TK Interview and More
description:
Friday 9/29 Today on the show we had our good friend Tank come by. And you know when Tank shows up some type of freaky discussion is bound to come up, perfect for Freaky Friday. This time around we definitely needed him to clear up a statement that definitely had people question his sexuality. Also, we had comedian TK Kirkland come by to promote his comedy show this week. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a girl that got purple ink injected in her eye.
